      <title>About Transactions and self</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/about-transactions-and-self/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/about-transactions-and-self/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5296-about-transactions-and-self.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;About Transactions and self&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;About Transactions and self 
    &lt;div id=&#34;about-transactions-and-self&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#about-transactions-and-self&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From our experience we say&lt;br&gt;
Doing transaction of any kind &lt;br&gt;
Whether social, commercial, religious &lt;br&gt;
We need another &lt;br&gt;
But if we don&amp;rsquo;t know about another &lt;br&gt;
Then transaction can be risky &lt;br&gt;
It can cause pain, hurt, loss or suffering &lt;br&gt;
Therefore don&amp;rsquo;t transact with unknown. &lt;br&gt;
(a frequently used proverb)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But, how do we know someone without transacting?&lt;br&gt;
After transaction only we know &lt;br&gt;
Transaction with unknown person maybe good or bad.&lt;br&gt;
But the same applies to your known &lt;br&gt;
If you know someone and then transact &lt;br&gt;
In that case also transaction maybe good or bad.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
