&lt;p&gt;Depending upon the context and situation  &lt;br&gt;
the answer can vary but if you analyze the answer  &lt;br&gt;
then you will find the answer is referring  &lt;br&gt;
to objects and concepts around the answerer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
